metadata.description:
If you buy a Coffee Nova NFT, you can become an Exclusive Affiliate, and can register for an affiliate code. What this means is that customers must use an affiliate code in order to make a purchase. If a customer does not have an affiliate code, they can choose a random one, ensuring an affiliate will always receive the sales commission. 

Our goal is to create a robust, decentralized community of affiliates who can earn passive income on their own terms, growing as Coffee Nova grows.
metadata.name: Coffee Nova NFT
